title: Society's Brainwash
itunes:title: Society's Brainwash
description:
Episode 244 - In society we are raised to fit in - to sit down, shut up, speak when spoken to, raise your hand to speak, etc. That type of mindset does not make a successful rebel. Listen to this episode to learn how to not fit in to be successful.
